ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v281.group

Class EHC_E10_PSGPSLADJ

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractStructure
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractGroup
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v281.group.EHC_E10_PSGPSLADJ
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Group, Structure, Visitable, Serializable

    public class EHC_E10_PSGPSLADJ
extends AbstractGroup

    Represents a EHC_E10_PSGPSLADJ group structure (a Group object). A Group is an ordered collection of message segments that can repeat together or be optionally in/excluded together. This Group contains the following elements:

    • 1: PSG (Product/Service Group)
    • 2: EHC_E10_PRODUCT_SERVICE_LINE_INFO (a Group object) repeating
